info.name: CYLTabBarController
info.description: [EN]It is an iOS UI module library for adding animation to iOS tabbar items and icons with Lottie, and adding a bigger center UITabBar Item.  [CN]【中国特色 TabBar】一行代码实现 Lottie 动画TabBar，支持中间带+号的TabBar样式，自带红点角标，支持动态刷新。【iOS13 & Dark Mode  & iPhone XS MAX supported】
